c8e88c7f2f189f3417339e53a3fd0829:
query QContractQuery(
  $subscriberId: ID!
) {
  contract(subscriberId: $subscriberId) {
    externalId
    effectDate
    numberOfBeneficiaries
    subscriber {
      civility
      firstName
      lastName
      fullName
      birthName
      birthDate
      nic
      address
      zipCode
      city
      email
      phone
    }
    beneficiaries {
      externalId
      civility
      firstName
      lastName
      fullName
      nic
      birthDate
    }
    payments {
      iban
      ribUploadId
      ribFilename
    }
  }
}
